text.tspan: Ive has always had a passion for creativity. Drawing, designing,
planning, and engineering since I was young. During my time
studying Computer Science at MSU Denver, I found I could
combine my creativity with code to create beautiful user
experiences, and it felt like the perfect place to express myself
and have a real impact on people.
Im a self starter, hard worker, and all around a down to earth
person who loves being outside. My hobbies are what give me
life, so I founded a coffee roasting business during college that I
branded and built an e-commerce site for orders with, which was
a huge learning experience. During that time I worked as an
intern at Agency Technology building an API to provide
automated software solutions for the travel industry, where I
learned what working in a professional environment was like and
how important team organization is.
Before graduating in May of 2021, I had the opportunity to work
on an amazing team of students to develop Talon Agency, a site
for digital, comprehensive background checks. Which served as
our senior project and a representation of my frontend skills and
how they are progressing daily.
Now that leaves me off where I am today, looking to learn, grow,
and create in a way that impacts people positively. If you want to
help me on this journey please contact me!
